# Enforce LF line endings repo-wide so checkouts are identical on every OS.
# Without this, autocrlf=true on Windows yields CRLF working-tree files, which
# diverge from the LF the toolchain (gofmt, golangci-lint, the code generator)
# expects — causing local-vs-CI mismatches.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicit binary types (never normalize) — add more as needed.
*.png binary
*.ico binary
*.icns binary
*.gz binary
*.zip binary
